&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Use of Artificial Intelligence (AI):&lt;br&gt;No AI or automated decision-making tools are used to screen, assess, or select candidates for this role. Our company uses the Greenhouse applicant tracking system, which does not apply AI in these parts of the hiring process.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
