&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education&lt;/strong&gt;: High School Diploma or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&lt;/strong&gt;: 1+ years of prior work experience (Hospitality, Retail, or Office Services experience is a major plus!).&lt;/li&gt;
