&lt;li&gt;Excellent customer service skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PC skills MS Office Suite experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle multiple tasks simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
